summary: This Mod turns Jenassea from the Drunken Huntsman into a Khajiit Follower.
descriptionHtml:
This Mod turns Jenassea from the Drunken Huntsman into a Khajiit Follower.

Just Copy the Contents of this Archieve to your Skyrim/Data Folder, after this you have to enable the Plugin in your Skyrim Launcher.

Thats all.

Greetings, Khajiirah!


[b][u]Optional:[/u]
For the Body Texture use "Khajiit Leopard Texture" CBBE or UNP here from Nexus.[/b]
author: Khajiirah aka Ahrwen
